    Iowa. He is the author of <i>The Peculiar Democracy: Southern Democrats in 
    Peace and Civil War</i> (2001). He currently is working on a study of Stonewall 
    Jackson’s image in American culture. 
    <P> 
    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> Formerly a historic site 
