    and supporter of John Brown, <i>The Making of 'Mammy Pleasant': A Black Entrepreneur 
    in Nineteenth-Century San Francisco</i> (University of Illinois Press, 2003). 
    <P> 
    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Peter A. Huff</b> holds 
