    War, and Remembrance in the Appalachian South</i> (forthcoming), and co-edited 
    essay collections on Unionists in the Civil War South and on Confederate nationalism. 
    <p> 
    <font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>John Jakes</b><b><a name="janda"></a></b> 
