    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><B>Michael Morrison</b> 
    is author of <i>Slavery and the American West: The Eclipse of Manifest Destiny 
    and the Coming of the Civil War</i> (1997). He is currently writing a comprehensive 
    study of how the Mexican American War and the Mexican Cession began the transformation 
    of the two-party Jacksonian system into the sectional politics of the 1850s. 
    <p> 
    <font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>Bob Mrazek</b> is the 
