    Journals of Judge William Barclay Napton, 1829-1883</i> (Columbia: University 
    of Missouri Press, 2005). His current project is a study of the Civil War 
    on the middle border and its social and cultural effects on regional identity, 
    to be published by Oxford University Press. 
