    of eight books on military and naval history including, most recently, <I>Confederate 
    Admiral: The Life and Wars of Franklin Buchanan</I> (1999). 
    <p><b><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2">Marc J. Storch</font></b> 
    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"> 
    is the author of several articles on the Civil War and a co-author with his 
    wife of an essay in the book<I> Giants in Their Tall Black Hats: Essays in 
    the Iron Brigad</I>e (1998). They are currently working on a regimental study 
    of the 2nd Wisconsin Infantry. 
    <p> 
    <font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><b>Walter Sullivan</b>, 
