    <p> 
    <font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b>Richard Zuczek</b> is 
    an Associate Professor at the United States Coast Guard Academy. He has authored 
    and edited several works on Reconstruction, most recently the Encyclopedia 
    of the Reconstruction Era (2006). 
    <!-- end of content -->
